==French==

===Verb===
'''régler'''
# To [[sort out]], to [[settle]] (a problem, a bill)
#:''On va régler le problème tout de suite.''
#::''We will sort out that probelm immediately.''
# To [[set]], to [[adjust]]
#:''Régler le réveil pour 8 heures.''
#::''Set the alarm for 8 o'clock.''
# To [[regulate]]
# To [[rule]]; to put lines on.
#:''Régler le papier.''

